    {
      "kind": "artifact",
      "id": "flowsheet-ghost-221",
      "reference": "flowsheet_document",
      "description": "Flowsheet 221 中包含 Feed Heater 602 (heater-3) 和 Flash Drum 602 (flash-15)。"
    },
    {
      "kind": "context",
      "field": "legal_candidate_completions[0]",
      "reference": "cand-heater-3-outlet-flash-15",
      "description": "候选连接：heater-3.outlet → flash-15.inlet，推荐流名 H-602。距离 65px，对齐分 0.94，拓扑分 0.91，但处于 dismiss 冷却期且要求手动重新选择。"
    },
    {
      "kind": "context",
      "field": "naming_hints",
      "description": "上游流名为 F-602，建议出口前缀 H，数字后缀 602，因此推荐流名 H-602。"
